{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An amare visual novel that focuses on what some have described as the \u201csecond\u201d coming-of-age, the ephemeral nature of relationships and the work it requires to understand and empathize with one another.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience life as it happens, each chapter defined by the events and choices you make for yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as one of four total personality types, changing aspects of your personality as the game continues. Forge close friendships, distance yourself from specific characters, bring in even more new faces, or choose love\u2014 that is, if you want to. Between an intricate system of impressions that depend on both the player\u2019s decisions and a chosen combination of events and experience, no one playthrough will be quite like the others.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hundreds of variations established via player choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play 3 of 5 possible events, in any order you choose (for a total of 60 possible combinations)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1+ CG per event (with variations based on in-game choices)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Partial voice acting &amp; original BGM</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In-story UI\u2014 use your phone to select events and text/call with other characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quick time events (input-based and timed-choice) for added variability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic relationships\u2014 not only do you choose your perceptions of other characters, but other characters also change their impressions of you based on your words and actions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reactive storytelling\u2014 dialogue and narration change in response to previously played events</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540650/pa